#. module: website
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:website.s_quotes_carousel_minimal
msgid ""
"\" A trusted partner for growth. <br/>Professional, efficient, and always "
"ahead of the curve. \""
msgstr ""
"\" ຄູ່ຮ່ວມງານທີ່ໄວ້ວາງໃຈໄດ້ເພື່ອການເຕີບໂຕ. <br/>ເປັນມືອາຊີບ, ມີປະສິດທິພາບ, ແລະ ກ້າວໜ້າສະເໝີ. \""

#. module: website
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:website.s_quotes_carousel_minimal
msgid ""
"\" Outstanding service and results! <br/>They exceeded our expectations in "
"every project. \""
msgstr ""
"\" ການບໍລິການ ແລະ ຜົນຮັບທີ່ໂດດເດັ່ນ! <br/>ພວກເຂົາເຮັດໄດ້ເກີນຄວາມຄາດໝາຍຂອງພວກເຮົາໃນທຸກໆໂຄງກາ"
"ນ. \""

#. module: website
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:website.s_quotes_carousel_minimal
msgid ""
"\" This company transformed our business. <br/>Their solutions are "
"innovative and reliable. \""
msgstr ""
"\" ບໍລິສັດນີ້ໄດ້ປ່ຽນແປງທຸລະກິດຂອງພວກເຮົາ. <br/>ວິທີການແກ້ໄຂຂອງພວກເຂົາແມ່ນມີຄວາມຄິດສ້າງສັນ ແລະ ເຊື່"
"ອຖືໄດ້. \""

#. module: website
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:website.s_blockquote
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:website.s_quotes_carousel
msgid ""
"\" Write a quote here from one of your customers. Quotes are a great way to "
"build confidence in your products or services. \""
msgstr ""
"\" ຂຽນຄຳຍ້ອງຍໍຈາກລູກຄ້າຄົນໜຶ່ງຂອງທ່ານຢູ່ບ່ອນນີ້. ຄຳຍ້ອງຍໍເປັນວິທີທີ່ດີໃນການສ້າງຄວາມເຊື່ອໝັ້ນໃຫ້ກັບຜະລິດຕະພັ"
"ນ ຫຼື ການບໍລິການຂອງທ່ານ. \""

#. module: website
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:website.bs_debug_view
msgid "\" alert with a"
msgstr "\" ແຈ້ງເຕືອນດ້ວຍ"

